f091ce9e87.mp4?t=1732359247\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Prepare for the bossfights!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2975270/extras/61ef17db24065b2e67afaf172e9303bd.poster.avif?t=1732359247\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2975270/extras/61ef17db24065b2e67afaf172e9303bd.webm?t=1732359247\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2975270/extras/61ef17db24065b2e67afaf172e9303bd.mp4?t=1732359247\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Meet the mysterious merchant</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2975270/extras/431fb99f0a829d992d65abddd2a29682.poster.avif?t=1732359247\" width=284 height=112 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2975270/extras/431fb99f0a829d992d65abddd2a29682.webm?t=1732359247\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2975270/extras/431fb99f0a829d992d65abddd2a29682.mp4?t=1732359247\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Features:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Strategic Inventory Management:</strong> Equip items from your hero's inventory to optimize their loadout for battle.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Weight Management:</strong> Keep an eye on the weight indicator to ensure your hero can carry all their gear without being burdened.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Potions and Belts:</strong> Combine potions and equip them on your hero's belt for quick access during combat.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Durability management:</strong> Equip optimal weapons to minimize their wear while the combat is resolved automatically.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Stat Allocation and Leveling:</strong> Allocate stat points as your hero levels up to suit your loadout.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Rare Item Abilities: </strong>Discover rare items with special abilities that can turn the tide of battle in your favor.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Merchant: </strong>Trade your items with the mysterious merchant.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
